data.description: ****OWNED SOLAR AND BATTERIES, PLUS WHOLE HOME FILTRATION WITH SOFTENER **** Peruse the highly coveted Borgata Floor Plan by Pulte, where each bedroom has an oversized walk-in closet. Entertain in the fully upgraded kitchen, which includes new appliances and an extended island with ample seating. This home has been fully upgraded, starting with the kitchen, lighting, 3cm quartz countertops, tile, belted garage door opener, and much more! Lower utility costs with Owned Solar plus storage batteries! A BONUS loft area provides a wonderful place for fun and relaxation. Easily converted to 5 BEDS No rear neighbors and a low-maintenance backyard with beautiful pavers and turf for a green look all year! The owner is a licensed agent in the state of Arizona.
